flowchart TD
    User -->|Start / Pause / Reset| SimulationController
    User -->|Change Parameters| SimulationController

    SimulationController --> TrafficManager
    SimulationController --> Renderer

    TrafficManager -->|Spawn Vehicles| VehicleFactory
    TrafficManager -->|Update Signals| TrafficSignalSystem
    TrafficManager -->|Manage Roads| RoadNetwork

    Vehicle -->|Subscribe| TrafficSignal
    TrafficSignal -->|Notify State Change| Vehicle

    Vehicle -->|Uses| PhysicsEngine
    PhysicsEngine --> IDMModel
    PhysicsEngine --> BrakingStrategy

    Renderer -->|Draw| Vehicle
    Renderer -->|Draw| RoadNetwork
    Renderer -->|Draw| TrafficSignal